Vulois is sitting with the TM3 driver trying to figure out some of 
it's functions before Soundwave arrives with the equipement to use 
it. He has already learend that it will give you a 3rd 
transformation. If you can already fly than you will get a tank mode. 
If you can't fly you will receive a jet mode. He checks the wiring, 
and it turns out it will double the strength of your weapons, double 
your speed and somewhat increase your ability to defend. Vulois can 
not wait until Soundwave shows up with the equipment. Everyone will 
be surprised....
